{"id":239621,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-成都访民陈茜遭软禁，疑为公安借此拿维/","date":"2012-07-13T04:01:07Z","modified":"2012-07-13T04:01:07Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民陈茜遭软禁，疑为公安借此拿维稳费（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李飞报道）四川成都市金牛区访民陈茜致电本网信息员称：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>分</span><span>，陈茜与丈夫下楼散步时，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>男</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>女将他们拦住不许出门，陈茜与他们理论，他们说不服打电话找金牛区人民北路派出所，他们会给你们解释，于是，陈茜打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，可</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>两小时后还未见出警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>据陈茜说：“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日下午，人民北路派出所新调来的所长和片警吴铭远拿来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>公斤</span><span>北大荒的大米说来看我们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>要我们去依法维权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>他们走后，成都另外两名访民到他们家玩耍后回家时发现，他们楼下有两台车六个人在门口把守，打电话告诉陈茜，陈茜没有理会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日早上陈茜下楼时发现有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>人看守在门口，陈茜没有理会，出门去了成都市信访局，并拿到了信访回执单。回家后就出现了文章开头的一幕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>陈茜对本网信息员说：“现在又不是什么敏感时期，我们也不需要去北京上访，我认为成都人民北路派出所这是公然限制人身自由、绑架政府，以此要维稳费。我们访民实际上已经成为公安的摇钱树”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>陈茜是因为法院非法强拆而上访维权的。他们于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1997</span><span>年金法行初字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>号胜诉，却在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1999</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月被金牛区法院违法强制执行，将其家产洗劫一空，从此走向上访之路。在上访过程中，多次被公安非法拘禁，数十次被关黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>经最高法院证实，陈茜提出的国家赔偿和金牛区法院非法强拆一案己转到最高人民法院国家赔偿委员会，最高法院预约时间是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>接谈陈茜，然后再决定是否赔偿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>据陈茜介绍：其实他们的案子在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年，地方政府就与他们达成意向性的会议纪要，由于街道政法委为了吃维稳费而久拖不落实。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年开始在金牛区副区长胡斌、建交局局长任务、人北街道书记黄清、房管局局长马德良等领导的协调下，定于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>交还铺面给陈茜他们经营，</span><span> </span><span>但人民北路派出所为了捞取维稳费，制造予盾，多方阻挠，逼她们去上访。“只要我们上访，我们就成为公安的摇钱树”陈茜说。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VfxBudaqQ9w/T_-CvridD6I/AAAAAAAAJOU/BqN4_NSocyM/s1600/%E9%99%88%E8%8C%9C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%83%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VfxBudaqQ9w/T_-CvridD6I/AAAAAAAAJOU/BqN4_NSocyM/s320/%E9%99%88%E8%8C%9C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%83%A8.JPG\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OTP8Fv9MBuE/T_-CxczpT6I/AAAAAAAAJOc/kGVOOwZ-8TI/s1600/%E9%99%88%E8%8C%9C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OTP8Fv9MBuE/T_-CxczpT6I/AAAAAAAAJOc/kGVOOwZ-8TI/s320/%E9%99%88%E8%8C%9C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2.JPG\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1252608606307441336?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/cc2f2445BEE983A8.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,9503]}